Paper: hep-th/9812111

Date: 1998-12-14

Title: The Secret Life of the Dipole

Comments: 6 pages, latex. A shorter version of this article, but with two

figures, appeared in Nature, vol. 387, 558-559 (5 June 1997)A new force on the magnetic dipole, which exists in the presence of bothelectric and magnetic fields, is described. Its origin due to the `hiddenmomentum', implications and possible experimental tests are discussed.